Angular Cheat Sheet

Angular install: npm install -g @angular/cli

new app: ng new appname 
  --> No rounting and plain CSS

run and compile: ng serve

new component: ng generate component compname 
  --> short ng g c compname

add modules: npm install --save @angular/material .....
  -->--save adds it tyo package.json as well. This way teammembers will get the correct libraries when pulling from Git.
  
  
